OL,3,CMan killed because he 'owed money to
OL,4,Cdealers who thought he was a
OL,5,Cpaedophile'
OL,7,FA Somerset father was murdered because
OL,8,Fhe owed money to drug dealers who also
OL,9,Fbelieved he was a paedophile, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FMichael Wheeler, 37, was himself a
OL,13,Fuser and dealer and would drive two of
OL,14,Fthe accused ` Angus Warner and Jack
OL,15,FRance - around Yeovil, prosecuting
OL,16,Fbarrister Devid Elias KC told Bristol
OL,17,FCrown court.
