OL,3,CMan killed because he 'owed money to
OL,4,Cdealers who thought he was a
OL,5,Cpaedophile'
OL,7,FIn August 2024, Mr Wheeler was so
OL,8,Fconcerned for his safety, he told his
OL,9,Fex-wife he had started carrying a
OL,10,Fknife.
OL,12,FThey had a video call late on 23
OL,13,FAugust in which he looked panicked and
OL,14,Frattled, she said. The call ended
OL,15,Fabruptly.
OL,17,FThe last thing he said was 'I love you
OL,18,Fprincess' and referring to their
OL,19,Fdaughter he said, 'tell that little
OL,20,Fgirl I love her.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
