OL,3,CMan killed because he 'owed money to
OL,4,Cdealers who thought he was a
OL,5,Cpaedophile'
OL,7,FHis car was seen crossing town and
OL,8,Fthen parked near Juniper Close, which
OL,9,Fwas where two other defendants, Mark
OL,10,FRoberts and David Garland, lived.
OL,12,FFor about an hour, neighbours heard
OL,13,Fshouting including 'we know you're a
OL,14,Fpaedophile, we've seen it online' and
OL,15,F'give us your money,' the jury was
OL,16,Ftold.
OL,18,FAnother neighbour was awoken by a man
OL,19,Fscreaming: 'Please leave me alone.
OL,20,FYou're going to kill me.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
