OL,5,Cpaedophile'
OL,7,FOne neighbour made notes of the names
OL,8,Fshe could hear being shouted: Dave,
OL,9,FReuben and Sparky ` which was the
OL,10,Fnickname of Mark Roberts. Reuben Clare
OL,11,Fis another of the men on trial.
OL,13,FPolice were called and an officer
OL,14,Fspoke with Mark Roberts outside the
OL,15,Fflat. Roberts said he didn't like the
OL,16,Fpolice and everything was okay. The
OL,17,Fpolice officer had no concerns, the
OL,18,Fcourt was told, and he left.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
