OL,5,Cpaedophile'
OL,7,FBut then just after three in the
OL,8,Fmorning Garland sent a photo to a
OL,9,Ffriend of Michael Wheeler sitting in
OL,10,Fthe flat, he was beaten and bruised.
OL,12,FA few days later, police in Yeovil
OL,13,Fcalled at Jack Rance's home and found
OL,14,Fdrugs. They arrested him and Warner `
OL,15,Fand during the search came across
OL,16,FMichael Wheeler's passport and the
OL,17,Fkeys to his car.
