OL,7,FMark Roberts's flat was later
OL,8,Fexamined, and stains of Michael
OL,9,FWheeler's blood was found along with a
OL,10,Fgolf club and baseball bat, Mr Elias
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FA month later, Mark Roberts informed
OL,14,Fpolice that he had been told Michael
OL,15,FWheeler's remains were in a caravan in
OL,16,FYarlington. A search there found Mr
OL,17,FWheeler's body. He had suffered,
OL,18,Feleven blows to the head.
